Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}抽泣的羊角面包! \N{\rENG}Sniffling Croissant!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.22,0:00:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你真是了解我啊 互联网\N{\rENG} You really know me, Internet.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嗨 伙计们! \N{\rENG} Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 怎么 史蒂文? \N{\rENG} Yeah, Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你们得试试我发现的这个在线测试\N{\rENG} You guys should take this online quiz I found.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.10,0:00:40.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 它会告诉你...\N{\rENG} It tells you what...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.78,0:00:45.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 它会得出你对应 "哭泣的早餐好友" 中的哪个角色!\N{\rENG} It tells you what character you are from "Crying Breakfast Friends"!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.38,0:00:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 额...为什么? \N{\rENG} Eh...Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 将你自己当作某个卡通人物来看待非常有趣\N{\rENG} It's just fun to see yourself as a cartoon character.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 像流泪的蛋杯 非常神经质和保守\N{\rENG} Like Weeping Eggcup, who's neurotic and uptight,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 或者伤心的葡萄柚 一个年长敏感的角色\N{\rENG} or Pining Grapefruit, the sensitive older one
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 希望自己是个更好的楷模\N{\rENG} who wishes he was a better role model.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.88,0:00:59.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 额 也许我们可以在修好车后做这个\N{\rENG} Uh, maybe we can do that thing after we've fixed the van.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.36,0:01:02.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧\N{\rENG} Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.54,0:01:03.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我去找别人试试! \N{\rENG} I'll go find someone else!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你理解得了那个卡通秀吗? \N{\rENG} Do you understand that cartoon show?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我已经跟不上时代了\N{\rENG} I don't understand anything anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嗨 史蒂文 还有机油吗? \N{\rENG} Hey, Steven. Is there any more engine oil?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.73,0:01:15.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我需要拿来配三明治\N{\rENG} I need it for this sandwich.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.56,0:01:17.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我...觉得那是给车的\N{\rENG} I...Think that's for cars.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那么 还有吗? \N{\rENG} Well, is there any more of it?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.74,0:01:21.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我爸在外面可能还有些\N{\rENG} Dad's probably got some outside.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦! 但 额 你一定得试试这个在线测试\N{\rENG} Oh! But, uh, you got to take this online quiz.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是哪个 "哭泣的早餐朋友"? \N{\rENG} Which Crying Breakfast Friend are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那个节目非常诡异\N{\rENG} That show's really weird.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.66,0:01:31.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 谁想看一个角色都在哭泣的卡通节目? \N{\rENG} Who wants to watch a cartoon about people crying?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我想! \N{\rENG} I do!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧 好吧! \N{\rENG} Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 额...第一个问题是什么? \N{\rENG} Uh...What's the first question?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是否曾草率行事? \N{\rENG} Do you ever act without thinking?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 没 从没有过\N{\rENG} Nope. Never.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是否害怕面对风险和尝试新事物? \N{\rENG} Are you afraid of taking risks and trying new things?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 超害怕\N{\rENG} Terrified.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶 你是认真的吗? \N{\rENG} Amethyst, are you taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 当然\N{\rENG} Of course I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧\N{\rENG} Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是否对人际关系\N{\rENG} Are you insecure about your relationships
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 和别人的看法感到不安? \N{\rENG} and how you're perceived by other people?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 不~\N{\rENG} Nnnno.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 对? 额...\N{\rENG} Yes? Eh...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.42,0:02:04.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 正确答案是什么? \N{\rENG} What's the right answer?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这没有正确答案\N{\rENG} There is no right answer.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你应该坦诚的回答\N{\rENG} You're just supposed to answer honestly.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 切 我受够了\N{\rENG} Nah, I'm bored.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 等等--我还有很多探讨性的个人问题要问你!\N{\rENG} Wait--I have loads more probing, personal questions to ask!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.58,0:02:17.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 石榴? 你-你在我屋里干嘛? \N{\rENG} Garnet! W-what are you doing in my room?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我看到一个堕转的宝石人\N{\rENG} I saw a corrupted gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我通过它在岩石中挖出的通道跟踪它\N{\rENG} I followed it through the tunnel it dug in the rock.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.14,0:02:22.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧\N{\rENG} Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 它来自哪里? \N{\rENG} Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 听起来像是珍珠描述的\N{\rENG} It's similar to Pearl's description
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 在神庙中偷偷游走的生物\N{\rENG} of the creature she saw slinking through the temple.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你看到了游走者?!\N{\rENG} You saw the slinker?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我以为我们都同意游走者不存在\N{\rENG} I thought we agreed there was no slinker
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 而且我们也不会管它叫 "游走者"\N{\rENG} and that we weren't going to call it "the slinker".
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 对 之前是的\N{\rENG} Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 但现在不可否认的是那个生物存在\N{\rENG} But now it's undeniable the creature exists
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 且就该用史蒂文的命名\N{\rENG} and that Steven's name stuck.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 对! \N{\rENG} Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 不! \N{\rENG} No!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 听着 为什么不直接让我去找它? \N{\rENG} Look, why don't you just let me look for it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 因为你不会去做\N{\rENG} Because you won't.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这东西在这里多久了? \N{\rENG} How long's this thing been in here?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 看 史蒂文! 我是个厚皮脸! \N{\rENG} Look, Steven! I'm a pachyderm!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 看! 开盖有惊喜哦! \N{\rENG} Oh! And there's a prize inside!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嘘! 安静\N{\rENG} Shhh! Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦 石榴 严肃但实际\N{\rENG} Oh, Garnet. Stern but practical.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.96,0:03:12.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 就像洒出的牛奶\N{\rENG} Just like spilt milk.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你不会还在想那个破动画吧? \N{\rENG} You're not still on about that dumb cartoon, are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦 对--测试! \N{\rENG} Oh, right--the quiz!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是否在别人询问你试图隐藏的情绪时\N{\rENG} Do you get defensive when people ask you questions
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.94,0:03:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 变得非常焦虑不安? \N{\rENG} about the feelings you prefer to keep hidden?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 别试图对我进行心理分析 史蒂文\N{\rENG} Don't get all psycho-logical on me, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 呃...抱歉? \N{\rENG} Uh...Sorry?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那里! \N{\rENG} There!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 喔! 你抓到了吗?!\N{\rENG} Whoa, mama! Did you get it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.92,0:03:45.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 不\N{\rENG} No.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嗷 天! \N{\rENG} Aw, man!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我想我最喜欢的圆形物品在里面\N{\rENG} I think my favorite round thing was in there.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我会给你找个新的圆形物品\N{\rENG} I'll get you a new round thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 啊! 你可是在折腾我的东西! \N{\rENG} Ugh! This is my stuff you're messing with!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 如果要--呃!--破坏的话 \N{\rENG} If it's gonna get--ugh!--Wrecked,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 也得由我来破坏! \N{\rENG} I'm gonna be the one to wreck it!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 看到没?!\N{\rENG} See?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 就该这么完--\N{\rENG} That's how it's do--
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶被打爆了! \N{\rENG} Amethyst got poofed!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 游走者! \N{\rENG} Slinker!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.24,0:04:28.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 石榴? \N{\rENG} Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 史蒂文 记着--我们的身体只是幻象\N{\rENG} Steven, remember--our bodies are only an illusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶不会有事的\N{\rENG} Amethyst will be fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 但-但-但珍珠花了整整两周才回来\N{\rENG} B-b-but Pearl took two whole weeks to come back.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 而我已经非常想念紫晶了! \N{\rENG} And I already miss Amethyst so much!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 别担心 她转眼间就会回来的\N{\rENG} Don't worry. She'll be back before you know it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 真的\N{\rENG} Literally.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶回来了! 紫晶回来了! \N{\rENG} Amethyst's back! Amethyst's back!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 看来你...相比之前多长了几条腿!\N{\rENG} Looks like you...Grew a few feet since the last time I saw you!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那真有点快了\N{\rENG} That was fast.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 即使是你\N{\rENG} Even for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 切! 这不算什么\N{\rENG} Eh! It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我可不想让我的头号粉丝等着\N{\rENG} I didn't want to keep my biggest fan waiting.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧 好吧! \N{\rENG} Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我们有游走者要游走! \N{\rENG} We got a slinker to slink!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.02,0:05:29.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 如果我是个怪物我会去哪? \N{\rENG} Where would I go if I was a monster?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嘿! 这里\N{\rENG} Hey! Over here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你的新形态很有意思嘛\N{\rENG} Your new form is really interesting.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 谢谢 史蒂文\N{\rENG} Thanks, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我都想不出你回来后会有这么大差别\N{\rENG} I didn't even know you could come back this different.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 谢谢 史蒂文\N{\rENG} Thanks, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那么 你为什么要长四条腿? \N{\rENG} So, why'd you come back with four legs?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 因为我喜欢走路! \N{\rENG}'Cause I like walking!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 喔 我也想要四条腿! \N{\rENG} Wow. I want four legs, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 不 你可不想\N{\rENG} No, you don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶对重生操之过急了\N{\rENG} Amethyst rushed her regeneration.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她本该多花点功夫的\N{\rENG} She should have taken her time.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 就像珍珠? \N{\rENG} Like Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.00,0:05:59.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 对 珍珠多花了点...精力在重生上\N{\rENG} Yes. Pearl put a bit more...Thought into how she came back.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 破 破 破! \N{\rENG} Pearl, Pearl, Pearl!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你知道我能听到你! \N{\rENG} You know I can hear you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我很抱歉不像珍珠那样花哨\N{\rENG} I'm sorry I'm not like Pearl with her fancy form
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 房间整洁 没有怪物\N{\rENG} and her clean room with no monsters in it.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶? \N{\rENG} Amethyst?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶的宝石! \N{\rENG} Amethyst's gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她又被打爆了! \N{\rENG} She got poofed again!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这对她是个好机会\N{\rENG} This is a good opportunity for her.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 现在她可以制造个更好的形态\N{\rENG} Now she can make a better form.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她回来了! \N{\rENG} She's coming back!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.38,0:06:29.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 没错 这次好多了! \N{\rENG} You're right. This is much better!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她在模仿珍珠! \N{\rENG} She's doing Pearl!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嘿 石榴 你认为我的新长相怎么样 石榴? \N{\rENG} Hey, Garnet. What do you think of my new look, Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我现在更像是珍珠了 这不好吗? 哈! \N{\rENG} I'm more like Pearl now. Isn't it wonderful? Ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我感觉实用般的完美! \N{\rENG} I feel practically perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我们得集中精力倾听那个怪物的动静\N{\rENG} We need to focus on listening for the creature.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦 但我没法集中精力\N{\rENG} Oh, but I can't focus.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 所有的这些石头尺寸都不同\N{\rENG} All these rocks are different sizes.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我们得按照形状和颜色对石头进行分类\N{\rENG} We'll have to organize them by shape and color.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.62,0:07:01.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 就没人告诉大自然我想让它长什么样吗? \N{\rENG} Didn't anyone tell nature how I want it to look?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 别鼓励她\N{\rENG} Don't encourage her.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 但我需要鼓励 石榴\N{\rENG} But I need encouragement, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我需要所有人持续的认同\N{\rENG} I need everyone's constant approval.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我必须要用嗔嗔的语调才能显摆我的...\N{\rENG} I need to loquaciously converse so I can show off...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 聪明才智\N{\rENG} How smart I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你可以跟我对话\N{\rENG} You can converse with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 让我们完成这个测试吧\N{\rENG} Let's finish that quiz.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你需要在行动前事先准备吗? \N{\rENG} Do you need to plan ahead before you act?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦 非常仔细\N{\rENG} Oh, thoroughly.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是否沉醉于微小细节? \N{\rENG} Do you obsess over little details?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 完全非常正确! \N{\rENG} Completely entirely!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 喔 你真是有条理啊\N{\rENG} Wow, you're so method.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}  你下次重生时能变成我吗? \N{\rENG} Next time, can you come back as me?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这对你不是个合适的形态\N{\rENG} This is not a good choice for your form.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 放松点 石榴\N{\rENG} Lighten up, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 就开不起玩笑嘛? \N{\rENG} Can't you take a joke?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这并不好笑\N{\rENG} It's not funny.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你让自己变得荒谬\N{\rENG} You've made yourself ridiculous.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 荒谬?!\N{\rENG} Ridiculous?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 小声点! 那个生物还在\N{\rENG} Keep your voice down! The creature.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你想让我学习珍珠 而现在我做到了! \N{\rENG} You wanted me to be more like Pearl, and now I am!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 珍珠会更严肃的对待自己的重生! \N{\rENG} Pearl would have taken her regeneration seriously!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你关心什么?!我的形态是我自己的事! \N{\rENG} What do you care?!My form is my business!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 只要事关团队的力量就跟我有关! \N{\rENG} It's my business when it affects the strength of the team!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那怎么?!我还不够强壮吗? \N{\rENG} So what?!I'm not strong enough?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶! \N{\rENG} Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你是说我很弱吗?!\N{\rENG} Are you saying I'm weak?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我对此渐渐麻木很奇怪吗? \N{\rENG} Is it weird I'm getting numb to this?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.78,0:08:17.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧! \N{\rENG} Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你看 我一开始不这么想 \N{\rENG} You know, I wasn't feeling this at first,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 但我回心转意了\N{\rENG} but I think I might be coming around!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 呦 史蒂仔 我看起来怎么样? \N{\rENG} Yo, ste-man. My seams straight?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那个新形态...让你舒服吗? \N{\rENG} Does that new form...Hurt you?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 当然\N{\rENG} No.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.99,0:08:32.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 嘿 石榴\N{\rENG} Hey, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你觉得这个配的怎么样? \N{\rENG} How'd you like to mix it up with this?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我就是随便拼凑了一下 你知道的\N{\rENG} Just a little something I threw together. You know.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 这个形态不稳定 紫晶\N{\rENG} This form isn't sustainable, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 但...是你说我要更强壮的! \N{\rENG} But...You're the one who said I needed to be stronger!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 好吧 如果是我的怪兽 那么就由我来处理\N{\rENG} Okay, if it's my monster, then I'll deal with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶! \N{\rENG} Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 待在我什么后! \N{\rENG} Stay behind me!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶! \N{\rENG} Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 紫晶! \N{\rENG} Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 放手! \N{\rENG} Let it go!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 不! \N{\rENG} No!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 是你想让我变强的! \N{\rENG} You wanted me to be stronger!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我照做了! \N{\rENG} I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我变成了你想要的样子! \N{\rENG} I'm being what you want!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我不想要这样! \N{\rENG} I don't want this!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 那么 你想怎么样?!\N{\rENG} Well, what do you want?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 告诉我 我会照做! \N{\rENG} Just tell me, and I'll do that!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我没法告诉你 紫晶! \N{\rENG} I can't tell you, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 你得自己想明白! \N{\rENG} You have to figure this out for yourself!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她做不到\N{\rENG} She can't.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她不想认识自己! \N{\rENG} She doesn't want to think about herself!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 什么? \N{\rENG} What?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.00,0:10:01.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 接得不错\N{\rENG} Good catch.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我就知道那东西是真的! \N{\rENG} I knew that thing was real!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 当紫晶回来后 我们得找到它\N{\rENG} When Amethyst gets back, we have to go find it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 已经过了多久了? \N{\rENG} How long has it been?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 四个小时\N{\rENG} Four hours.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 四个小时?!她从没花过这么久\N{\rENG} Four hours?!She's never taken so long.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 她在里面做什么? \N{\rENG} What is she doing in there?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 我不确定 我对她太苛刻了\N{\rENG} I'm not sure. I was too hard on her.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS} 哦 噢! 她要回来了! \N{\rENG} Oh, oh! She's coming back!
